@mitsudome-r  `CMakeLists.txt` created by catkin_make will cause `colcon build` to fail. For this reason `colcon_release` script removes the conflicting file. Read [here](https://github.com/CPFL/Autoware/pull/1704#issuecomment-448499700)

Many users didn't know about this, so it was added [here](https://github.com/CPFL/Autoware/commit/f77b7849273cffdbb5cc2583527c77d691572c45#diff-95aeef3f37fbf0a665ee13518909a061R12) and improved [here](https://github.com/CPFL/Autoware/commit/c42a9001da383ac75f8b1665e06f937c499ab27e#diff-95aeef3f37fbf0a665ee13518909a061R4) 

The instructions in the wiki are for `master` branch. These will be updated once the 1.11 is released.

